column2: "It's not here either. Damn it, what's going on?"
"There should be some kind of trace around here, did someone take it away?"
"You again? You didn't have enough fun with that robot? You really are a pain."
"And that little brat with you, it's also our second meeting, if I recall?"
"It's not the second time at all!"
"Dark Falz, that body you're in, you got it just about ten years ago, right?"
"You? How do you know that?"
"That's what I thought. I knew I recognized your face."
"Speak so that I can understand, otherwise, I'll kill you."
"You really don't remember, do you? I've been searching for you all this time!"
"Been searching?"
"Your gesture just now, it's not going well so you're agitated, right?"
"What are you getting at?"
"You've always been like that! Going off on your own and getting lost. Losing something and making me find it!"
"You're disgustingly similar! You're exactly like her!"
"Explain to me what you're getting at right now!"
"Fine, I'll explain it. The name of your host is Yucrita."
"Ten years ago, my sister was taken away before my eyes by a black figure!"
"Yucrita... sis-ter...!!! Damn it, my head!"
"Give her back! Give me back Yucri-sis!"
"Silence! Don't call me by that name!"
"He's worried about me? He should mind his own business."
"Wait! What the hell is going on!!?"
